    { "@type": "Question", "name": "What are the highest-scoring Scrabble words with MM?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "MAMMOTH (16 pts), SWIMMING (16 pts), and FLAMMABLE (18 pts) are top MM scorers. MM words tend to be longer (6-9 letters) and combine well with other mid-value consonants for strong overall scores." }},
