    { "@type": "Question", "name": "What patterns commonly contain MM in Scrabble?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "MM frequently appears in -MMER (HAMMER, SHIMMER, STAMMER, SUMMER), -MMING (SWIMMING, DRUMMING, HUMMING), -MMAND (COMMAND, DEMAND), and -MMON (COMMON, SUMMON). These longer patterns make MM a bingo-friendly combination." }}
  ]
})} />

