<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Words Containing Double M (MM) — Scrabble Scoring Guide</h1>

<div class="not-prose mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-400">
  <time datetime="2026-06-15">June 15, 2026</time>
  <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-300 dark:bg-gray-600"></span>
  <span>5 min read</span>
</div>

<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">MM words tend to be longer and more impressive than other double-letter words. While BLUFF and CLIFF keep things short, MM naturally gravitates toward 6-8 letter words — HAMMER, MAMMOTH, SWIMMING, COMMAND. This makes MM one of the best double-letter pairs for reaching bingo length, and each M contributes a solid 3 points to the total.</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">MM at a Glance</h2>

<div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
  <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-center">
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">6 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">MM base value (3+3)</p></div>
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">160+</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Valid MM words</p></div>
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">6–8</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Typical word length</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Top Scoring MM Words</h2>

<div class="overflow-x-auto not-prose my-6">
